name: BlueberrySky
0:
”Alexa, open blueberry sky”
”Alexa, ask blueberry sky air”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: blueberry sky
des:
Air in Seoul is sometimes bad for health filled with PM2.5 dust and it is helpful to check the air quality before going out. 

When you open Blueberry Sky, it gives you Air Quality Index which is from http://aqicn.org/city/seoul/kr/.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
